  "detailed_description": "<h1>Twitter</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1343750/extras/6cc8a9e410d9aba921c3a93ca45510d3.avif?t=1688471955\" width=609 height=336 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>THE MOST FUN VR HAND RACING</strong></h2>You're a racer from the future. Speed ​​is your passion and purpose in life. Super fast racing ships and futuristic tracks make this game an unforgettable experience. Improve your skills, unlock new ships and take top spot on the leaderboard.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><strong>COMFORTABLE VR EXPERIENCE</strong><br>We go the extra mile to ensure that Z-Race is the most comfortable VR racing game ever. Collect nitro boosts and coins, avoid energy traps and obstacles, overtake competitors with minimal motion sickness. A game for all ages, both kids and adults can play it!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1343750/extras/cf17a29d7abe7c48e9ec12d3419d403c.poster.avif?t=1688471955\" width=620 height=213 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1343750/extras/cf17a29d7abe7c48e9ec12d3419d403c.webm?t=1688471955\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>ASYNCHRONOUS MULTIPLAYER</strong></h2>Go head to head with anyone thanks to our asynchronous multiplayer. You will never be alone with the ghosts of your friends and strangers. In virtual reality, this is the best opportunity to always compete with worthy opponents.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1343750/extras/64b649fc02c1d53402be6205b9ff6157.avif?t=1688471955\" width=610 height=316 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1343750/extras/a3ce2995bb63fa8e8fe18d12fadfb9b9.poster.avif?t=1688471955\" width=620 height=213 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1343750/extras/a3ce2995bb63fa8e8fe18d12fadfb9b9.webm?t=1688471955\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FULLY IMMERSIVE AUDIO</strong></h2>What's a VR racing experience without some intense heart rate music? We've carefully selected the in-game music to ensure that you will feel the rythm of the game pumping through your veins. We've also included unique trainers with the voices of your favourite VR creators!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>MARVELOUS TRACKS</strong></h2>New ships and track become available during playthrough. The better you do, the more you will unlock. Upgrade your ships speed, agility, and nitro capacity via in-game currency.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1343750/extras/759e94ea0ad49592600007f4e946b437.poster.avif?t=1688471955\" width=620 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1343750/extras/759e94ea0ad49592600007f4e946b437.webm?t=1688471955\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>",
